quran[9{c,v,t}:
10,98,phir kya aisi koi misaal hai ke aik bastii azaab dekh kar imaan layi ho aur is ka imaan is ke liye naffa bakhash saabit howa ho? Younis ki qoum ke siwa ( is ki koi nazeer nahi ) woh qoum jab imaan le aayi thi to Albata hum ne is par se duniya ki zindagi mein ruswai ka azaab taall diya tha aur is ko aik muddat taq zindagi se behra mand honay ka mauqa day diya tha
10,99,agar tairay rab ki Mushiyat yeh hoti ( ke zameen mein sab momin o farmanbardar hi hon ) to saaray ahal zameen imaan le aeye hotay phir kya to logon ko majaboor kere ga ke woh momin ho jayen ?
10,100,"koi mutnaqas Allah ke azan ke baghair imaan nahi laa sakta, aur Allah ka tareeqa yeh hai ke jo log aqal se kaam nahi letay woh un par gandagi daal deta hai"
10,101,"inn se kaho “zamin aur asmano mein jo kuch hai usay ankhen khol kar dekho"" aur jo log imaan lana hi nahi chahtay un ke liye nishanain aur tambihain (warnings) aakhir kya mufeed ho sakti hain"
10,102,"ab yeh log iss ke siwa aur kis cheez ke muntazir hain ke wohi buray din dekhen jo inn se pehlay guzray hue log dekh chuke hain? inn se kaho “achha, intzaar karo, mein bhi tumahray sath intzaar karta hon """
10,103,phir ( jab aisa waqt aata hai to ) hum apne Rasolo-n ko aur unn logon ko bacha liya karte hain jo imaan laaye hon hamara yahi tareeqa hai hum par yeh haq hai ke mominon ko bacha len
10,104,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! keh do ke logo, agar tum abhi taq mere deen ke mutaliq kisi shak mein ho to sun lau ke tum Allah ke siwa jin ki bandagi karte ho mein un ki bandagi nahi karta balkay sirf isi khuda ki bandagi karta hon jis ke qabzay mein tumhari mout hai mujhe hukum diya gaya hai ke mein imaan laane walon mein se hon"
10,105,"aur mujh se farmaya gaya hai ke to yaksu ho kar apne aap ko theek theek iss deen par qaim kar day, aur hargiz hargiz mushrikon mein se nah ho"
10,106,aur Allah ko chore kar kisi aisi hasti ko nah pukaar jo tujhe nah faida pouncha sakti hai nah nuqsaan agar to aisa kere ga to zaalmon mein se hoga
